      "id": "short-mechanism",
      "durationMs": 35500,
      "narration": {
        "text": "PR #5227 is for card issuers: banks and fintechs whose users want to add their cards to Apple Wallet. Apple supports this from inside the Wallet app itself (the \"From apps on your iPhone\" section), but it requires shipping an issuer-provisioning app extension, a separate binary with a strict contract."
      },
